dc_title_s: Plan to Accompany Application of Andrew W. and Richard B. Mellon for a Riparian Grant on Newton Beach
dc_description_s: Map covers area along Newton Creek from the West Jersey and Seashore Railroad to Mt. Ephriam Ave. |Map shows Newton Creek, the high water line, low water line, and the edge of the meadow line. Map shows the land of Andrew W. and Richard B. Mellon
